### Get All Routes (Public Endpoint)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/public/routes
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Routes with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/public/routes?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Routes with Difficulty Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/public/routes?difficulty=moderate
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Routes with Search Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/public/routes?search=mountain
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Routes with Multiple Filters
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/public/routes?page=1&limit=5&difficulty=hard&search=trail
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Note: This public endpoint now returns only public user information (id and name)
# Sensitive information like email, created_at, is_active, etc. are hidden for privacy 